Alice Jules excellent coffee and delightful staff have become part of my routine, and I can’t imagine being without either.

I am so in love with this place. We were taking a drive from Charlotte with no destination. We drove by the cutest coffee shop with antique store next door. We had to stop and have some coffee. When I say cutest, I mean like Gilmore Girls set cute!

The place was all decorated with pumpkins and Halloween crafts. I mean they even had a Cousin Itt! Cousin Itt has never looked this good!

As for the owner and baristas? They were the kindest. Even though they were closing, they chased us down and offered us some coffee anyway. We sat outside on the patio and just had the best time.

I 100% recommend stopping by and will no doubt drive 30+ minutes to experience this again.
